thread.title: Kayli

author: Kayli
title: Kayli
text: My only complaint was that I got an email saying one of my books was not in good enough condition to be accepted. All my books were in good condition so I asked why it didn't pass inspection, and then got another email saying after repeat inspection it passed. Just wasn't sure why they weren't going to except it the first time! But good other than that!
